{"data":[{"name":"107:1","price":"1. (நபியே!) கூலி கொடுக்கும் நாளைப் பொய்யாக்குபவனை நீர் (கவனித்துப்) பார்த்தீரா?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6198,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"ara-ayta alladhī yukadhibu bil-dīni ","translations":["Have you seen","the one who","denies","the Judgment","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["ara-ayta","alladhī","yukadhibu","bil-dīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,1670],[3,1670,2990],[4,2990,6185]]}},{"name":"107:2","price":"2. (ஆதரவற்ற) அநாதைகளை வெருட்டுபவன் அவன்தான்.","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6199,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fadhālika alladhī yaduʿʿu al-yatīma ","translations":["Then that","(is) the one who","repulses","the orphan","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["fadhālika","alladhī","yaduʿʿu","al-yatīma",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1150],[2,1150,2000],[3,2000,2770],[4,2770,6435]]}},{"name":"107:3","price":"3. அவன் ஏழைகளுக்கு (உணவளிக்காததுடன்) உணவளிக்கும்படி (பிறரைத்) தூண்டுவதுமில்லை.","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6200,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"walā yaḥuḍḍu ʿalā ṭaʿāmi al-mis'kīni ","translations":["And (does) not","feel the urge","to","feed","the poor","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["walā","yaḥuḍḍu","ʿalā","ṭaʿāmi","al-mis'kīni",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,760],[2,760,1730],[3,1730,2240],[4,2240,3150],[5,3150,7145]]}},{"name":"107:4","price":"4. (கவனமற்ற) தொழுகையாளிகளுக்கும் கேடுதான்.","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6201,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fawaylun lil'muṣallīna ","translations":["So woe","to those who pray","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["fawaylun","lil'muṣallīna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,930],[2,930,5365]]}},{"name":"107:5","price":"5. அவர்கள் தங்கள் தொழுகைகளை விட்டும் மறந்தவர்களாக இருக்கிறார்கள்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6202,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum ʿan ṣalātihim sāhūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","about","their prayers","(are) neglectful","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","ʿan","ṣalātihim","sāhūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1290],[2,1290,1680],[3,1680,2430],[4,2430,4090],[5,4090,7475]]}},{"name":"107:6","price":"6. (மேலும்,) அவர்கள் (தொழுதபோதிலும் மக்களுக்குக்) காண்பிக்கவே தொழுகிறார்கள்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6203,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhīna hum yurāūna ","translations":["Those who","[they]","make show","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhīna","hum","yurāūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1230],[2,1230,1690],[3,1690,7455]]}},{"name":"107:7","price":"7. (மேலும், ஊசி போன்ற) அற்பப் பொருளையும் (இரவல் கொடுக்காது) தடுத்துக் கொள்கிறார்கள்.","arabic":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6204,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wayamnaʿūna al-māʿūna ","translations":["And they deny","[the] small kindnesses","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wayamnaʿūna","al-māʿūna",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1500],[2,1500,6525]]}}],"chapter":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un","Chapter Al-Ma'un","Ma'un","Surah Ma'un","Chapter Ma'un","Al Ma'un","Surah Al Ma'un","Chapter Al Ma'un","Surah 107","Chapter 107","The Small Kindnesses","الماعون"],"version":{"key":"tamil_baqavi","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ta","version":"1.0.1","last_update":1609966800,"title":"Tamil Translation - Abdulhamid Albaqoi","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Tamil by Sh. Abdulhamid Albaqoi"}}